      • isElementaryFlow

        boolean isElementaryFlow()
        Returns true if this exchange is an elementary flow. An exchange describes an elementary flow if it has an input group or output group with value 4. Additionally exchanges with no input group AND no output group (impact assessment factors) are recognised as elementary flows.
